{"id":"482967","subject":"Dear managers, How well are you taking advantage of Smart Life\u0027s convenient features?","content":{"text":"\u003cbody\u003e\u003c!-- [DocumentBodyStart:de29d97b-a216-4126-9b72-98904a1badec] --\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"jive-rendered-content\"\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"teaser\"\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"web-text\"\u003e\u003cp style\u003d\"min-height: 8pt; padding: 0px;\"\u003e\u0026#160;\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"teaser2\"\u003e \u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"p-content layoutBlock clearfix\" data-tpl\u003d\"text,text\"\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"column p-text p-one-second\"\u003e\u003cspan column\u003d\"column\" export-text\u003d\"\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"rte-text-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eManaging attendance for subordinates is an important task for managers, but it\u0027s also understandable that many feel burdened due to the abundance of information and the need for detailed checks within a limited time. For this time, we would like to introduce features that are essential to know and useful for efficient attendance management.\u003cbr type\u003d\"_moz\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"column lastBlock p-text p-one-second\"\u003e\u003cspan column\u003d\"column\" export-text\u003d\"\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"rte-text-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/showImage/102-482967-1-2304037/pastedImage_0.png\"\u003e\u003cimg alt\u003d\"\" class\u003d\"jive-image\" data-mce-src\u003d\"/servlet/JiveServlet/downloadImage/102-481847-1-2293612/pastedImage_0.png\" data-mce-style\u003d\"height: 155px; width: 175.489px;\" height\u003d\"155\" src\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/downloadImage/102-482967-1-2304037/175-155/pastedImage_0.png\" style\u003d\"width: 175.489px;\" width\u003d\"175\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"p-content layoutBlock clearfix\" data-tpl\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"column p-text p-one\"\u003e\u003cspan column\u003d\"column\" export-text\u003d\"\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"rte-text-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan style\u003d\"color: rgb(110, 160, 70);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e★Features you should know★\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr type\u003d\"_moz\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e１.To tracking what has been entered in the \"Details\"\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr type\u003d\"_moz\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHave you ever missed noticing that there was input for partial absence hours or reasons for the discrepancy between login/logout times on the \"Details\" screen? We have updated the display to make it easier to see the presence of input even from the \"Work Record Input\" screen.\u003cbr type\u003d\"_moz\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/showImage/102-482967-1-2304029/pastedImage_4.png\"\u003e\u003cimg alt\u003d\"\" class\u003d\"image-1 jive-image\" height\u003d\"125\" src\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/downloadImage/102-482967-1-2304029/pastedImage_4.png\" style\u003d\"width: auto; height: auto;\" width\u003d\"218\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"p-content layoutBlock clearfix\" data-tpl\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"column p-text p-one\"\u003e\u003cspan column\u003d\"column\" export-text\u003d\"\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"rte-text-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e２.To tracking actual annual paid leaves and leave plans\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHave you ever thought about wanting to efficiently get to know how many days of paid leave your subordinates have already taken and how many days of leave they have planned? You can review the details of actual leaves and plans from the \u0026ldquo;Fixed and planned paid leaves\u0026#8221; report.\u003cbr type\u003d\"_moz\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/showImage/102-482967-1-2304030/pastedImage_3.png\"\u003e\u003cimg alt\u003d\"\" class\u003d\"image-1 jive-image\" height\u003d\"222\" src\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/downloadImage/102-482967-1-2304030/pastedImage_3.png\" style\u003d\"width: 620px; height: 168px;\" width\u003d\"818\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"p-content layoutBlock clearfix\" data-tpl\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"column p-text p-one\"\u003e\u003cspan column\u003d\"column\" export-text\u003d\"\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"rte-text-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-mce-style\u003d\"color: #6ea046;\" style\u003d\"color: rgb(110, 160, 70);\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e★Useful Features You Might Want to Know★\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e１.Using data such as overtime hours, office attendance and mobile work frequency, etc. in Excel format\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHave you ever thought about wanting to check the overtime hours, number of times in the office and number of times for mobile work of your subordinates all at once? You can also check it on the \u0026ldquo;Monthly Approval of Work Record\u0026#8221; screen, but using the download feature at the bottom of the screen allows you to extract more detailed data in Excel format.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/showImage/102-482967-1-2304031/pastedImage_5.png\"\u003e\u003cimg alt\u003d\"\" class\u003d\"image-1 jive-image\" data-mce-src\u003d\"/servlet/JiveServlet/downloadImage/102-482967-2-2304031/pastedImage_5.png\" data-mce-style\u003d\"width: 620px; height: 85px;\" height\u003d\"112\" src\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/downloadImage/102-482967-1-2304031/pastedImage_5.png\" style\u003d\"width: 620px; height: 85px;\" width\u003d\"818\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"p-content layoutBlock clearfix\" data-tpl\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"column p-text p-one\"\u003e\u003cspan column\u003d\"column\" export-text\u003d\"\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"rte-text-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e２.Efficient checking when there are many inputs to Details\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr type\u003d\"_moz\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDo you spend a lot of time to open each \"Details\" pages on the web interface to check the input information? You can extract the input content in Excel format from the \u0026ldquo;Work Record Input\u0026#8221; screen using the download button. The input details from the \"Details\" screen are also included in the output, allowing you to have an overview of the information in a list.\u003cbr type\u003d\"_moz\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/showImage/102-482967-1-2304032/pastedImage_2.png\"\u003e\u003cimg alt\u003d\"\" class\u003d\"image-1 jive-image\" height\u003d\"237\" src\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/downloadImage/102-482967-1-2304032/pastedImage_2.png\" style\u003d\"width: 620px; height: 181px;\" width\u003d\"812\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"p-content layoutBlock clearfix\" data-tpl\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"column p-text p-one\"\u003e\u003cspan column\u003d\"column\" export-text\u003d\"\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"rte-text-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e３.Save the staff\u0027s timesheets on behalf\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr type\u003d\"_moz\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHave you ever been in a situation where you couldn\u0027t approve your subordinate\u0026#8217;s timesheets because he/she was absent and hadn\u0027t saved their timesheets, causing the status to remain \"Pending Approval\"? By setting yourself as the \"Daily Delegate Applicant\" for your staff member, you can save their timesheet and change its status to \"Pending Approval.\" (Please note that the \"Input by Delegate\" screen and the \"Work Approval\" screen are different, so make sure to switch screens for saving and approval.)\u003cbr type\u003d\"_moz\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/showImage/102-482967-1-2304033/pastedImage_2.png\"\u003e\u003cimg alt\u003d\"\" class\u003d\"image-1 jive-image\" height\u003d\"176\" src\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/downloadImage/102-482967-1-2304033/pastedImage_2.png\" style\u003d\"width: 620px; height: 142px;\" width\u003d\"771\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"p-content layoutBlock clearfix\" data-tpl\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"column p-text p-one\"\u003e\u003cspan column\u003d\"column\" export-text\u003d\"\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"rte-text-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e４.Filtering Feature for Regular Employee and Agency Staff\u003c/strong\u003e\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eHave you ever felt it\u0027s difficult to check when both regular staff and agency staff are mixed on the \"Monthly Approval of Work Record\" screen? You can use the agency staff filtering feature to display only regular employees or agency staff separately on the \" Monthly Approval of Work Record \" screen.\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/showImage/102-482967-1-2304038/pastedImage_0.png\"\u003e\u003cimg alt\u003d\"\" class\u003d\"image-1 jive-image\" height\u003d\"155\" src\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/downloadImage/102-482967-1-2304038/pastedImage_0.png\" style\u003d\"width: 620px; height: 142px;\" width\u003d\"678\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"p-content layoutBlock clearfix\" data-tpl\u003d\"text\"\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"column p-text p-one\"\u003e\u003cspan column\u003d\"column\" export-text\u003d\"\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv class\u003d\"rte-text-wrapper\"\u003e\u003cp\u003eHow many features did you know about? We hope you will use the useful features of SmartLife to support your efficient management!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e★SmartLife\u0027s time and attendance input/approval system is also available for smartphones.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eURL for Smartphone :\u003cbr type\u003d\"_moz\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/external-link.jspa?url\u003dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwb.wims-saas.jp%2Fz7DN9%2FWM01S001Init.do%3FLOCALE%3Den%26TERMINAL%3Dsp\" target\u003d\"_blank\"\u003ehttps://wb.wims-saas.jp/z7DN9/WM01S001Init.do?LOCALE\u003den\u0026amp;TERMINAL\u003dsp\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr type\u003d\"_moz\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/showImage/102-482967-1-2304040/pastedImage_4.png\"\u003e\u003cimg alt\u003d\"\" class\u003d\"jive-image\" data-mce-src\u003d\"/servlet/JiveServlet/downloadImage/102-481847-2-2293674/pastedImage_4.png\" data-mce-style\u003d\"width: 336px; height: 184.8px;\" height\u003d\"185\" src\u003d\"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/servlet/JiveServlet/downloadImage/102-482967-1-2304040/336-185/pastedImage_4.png\" style\u003d\"width:336px; height: 184.8px;\" width\u003d\"336\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c!-- [DocumentBodyEnd:de29d97b-a216-4126-9b72-98904a1badec] --\u003e\u003c/body\u003e"},"published":"2023-10-19T08:53:01.338+0000","updated":"2023-10-19T23:22:50.618+0000","author":{"id":"148893","displayName":"Akiko Yazawa","jive":{"enabled":true,"username":"AYAZAWA","visible":true},"type":"person"},"tags":[],"likeCount":2,"followerCount":1,"viewCount":18,"attachments":[],"contentImages":[{"id":"2304029","ref":"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/api/core/v3/images/2304029?a\u003d1697705584328","name":"pastedImage_4.png"},{"id":"2304030","ref":"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/api/core/v3/images/2304030?a\u003d1697705584333","name":"pastedImage_3.png"},{"id":"2304031","ref":"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/api/core/v3/images/2304031?a\u003d1697705584338","name":"pastedImage_5.png"},{"id":"2304032","ref":"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/api/core/v3/images/2304032?a\u003d1697705584343","name":"pastedImage_2.png"},{"id":"2304033","ref":"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/api/core/v3/images/2304033?a\u003d1697705584347","name":"pastedImage_2.png"},{"id":"2304037","ref":"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/api/core/v3/images/2304037?a\u003d1697705584352","name":"pastedImage_0.png"},{"id":"2304038","ref":"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/api/core/v3/images/2304038?a\u003d1697705738089","name":"pastedImage_0.png"},{"id":"2304040","ref":"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/api/core/v3/images/2304040?a\u003d1697757758322","name":"pastedImage_4.png"}],"parentPlace":{"id":"2867","html":"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/community/location/dta-en/daimler-trucks-asia-japan","name":"Mitsubishi Fuso Truck and Bus Corporation","uri":"https://uat.social.cloud.tbintra.net/api/core/v3/places/449039","type":"space"},"question":false,"restrictReplies":false,"type":"document"}